Sure, here are some examples of the Serbian word "nil" used in different forms and positions:

1. *Nil* je najduža reka na svetu. (The *Nile* is the longest river in the world.)
2. Planina je okružena gustim *nilovima*. (The mountain is surrounded by dense *nil* forests.)
