4. *Nilski* konj je najveći kopneni sisar u Africi. (The *hippopotamus* is the largest land mammal in Africa.)
5. Naša reprezentacija je ostvarila *nilski* rezultat na utakmici. (Our team achieved a *zero* result in the match.)
6. *Nilom* protiče kroz deset zemalja u Africi. (The *Nile* flows through ten countries in Africa.)
7. Ova knjiga je prevedena na *nilski* jezik. (This book has been translated into *Nilo-Saharan* language.)
8. *Nil* je vitalni izvor vode za Egipat. (The *Nile* is a vital source of water for Egypt.)
9. *Nilski* ostrvski jezici su prelepi turistički biseri. (The *Nile* island languages are beautiful tourist gems.)
10. Raspored u školi bio je potpuno *nilski* danas. (The school schedule was completely *empty* today.)

Note: In the examples above, the word "nil" has been used in various forms and meanings, such as the proper noun for the river Nile, the common noun for zero, the adjective meaning related to the Nile river, and the adjective meaning empty or zero.